    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/c11af44203db61e08d317bcb38433a53.webp?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合不同的<strong>职业</strong>和<strong>法术</strong>，与<strong>环境</strong>互动，以独特方式克服<strong>障碍</strong>与<strong>怪物</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点燃油坑？让水带电？把<strong>食尸鬼</strong>变成<strong>老鼠</strong>？或施放「静步术」，以完全<strong>潜行</strong>穿过地堡——一切取决于你的技巧与意志。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个<strong>职业</strong>都有自己的<strong>被动能力</strong>与<strong>法术</strong>。找到完美的组合，或组建全牧师小队，将<strong>真正的信仰</strong>带入地堡。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/c06d0d9363d95df48ab89c13a126cfac.poster.avif?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/c06d0d9363d95df48ab89c13a126cfac.webm?t=1772370467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/a8c4f52e912946dd6449295366572328.webp?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >施放<strong>法术</strong>会消耗你的<strong>信仰</strong>，并提升<strong>恐惧</strong>值。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某些<strong>上古恐怖</strong>也会吸取你的<strong>信仰</strong>。若失去平衡，<strong>她</strong>将现身；届时你会成为<strong>食尸鬼</strong>……或更糟的存在。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用酒精、队友的支援法术或<strong>照明</strong>来降低<strong>恐惧</strong>，保持<strong>发电机</strong>运转，并在任务中备点<strong>COPIUM</strong>。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/960619bf54f5921107fda9909465028e.poster.avif?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/960619bf54f5921107fda9909465028e.webm?t=1772370467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/c0a1ea5b028e1e705f13fe639bd53653.webp?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>缓缓推开</strong>门以确认陷阱；被追时就<strong>一脚踢开</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的每件物品都遵循物理：抓起、投掷，或直接从手中使用。就连被<strong>绊线</strong>触发的<strong>手榴弹</strong>也能丢开。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >队友可以在空中<strong>接住</strong>物品——<strong>但别朝他们扔已拉栓的手榴弹！</strong> 这样通常会让小队分崩离析……<strong>从四肢开始</strong>。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/ebb881cdc984a376040648577e506984.poster.avif?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/ebb881cdc984a376040648577e506984.webm?t=1772370467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/5cfead1f678e4c3ef750614f30c98aa1.webp?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >维持<strong>照明</strong>以驱散<strong>恐惧</strong>；或拥抱<strong>黑暗</strong>以换取更丰厚的奖励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发电机</strong>运转时，你的<strong>信仰</strong>会恢复，怪物也会稍微平静——但它也可能<strong>阻断通道</strong>，而通道后往往藏着珍贵的<strong>战利品</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次<strong>行动</strong>都会留下痕迹。击败<strong>首领</strong>或完成<strong>任务</strong>都会改变地图——不一定朝着好的一面。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/760e5d33837179d30976860817e5fa88.poster.avif?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/760e5d33837179d30976860817e5fa88.webm?t=1772370467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/a82aa3c7edd36a44ea66b4d90428a6b9.webp?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入另一个二战平行世界，柴油朋克科技与远古恐惧在此碰撞。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别害怕<strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong>：我们守住了<strong>信仰</strong>并尽力优化。任何卡顿都是纯粹的<strong>异端</strong>……或<strong>帝国之敌</strong>的手笔。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/2a0db6292bb99e8db53c640bf8f17876.poster.avif?t=1772370467\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/2a0db6292bb99e8db53c640bf8f17876.webm?t=1772370467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
